Gift list
<h2>Gift list</h2>

<p>Most of all, we would like you to join us on 21st September to celebrate our marriage.</p>

<p>If you would like to give a gift, you can find a gift list with John Lewis from 10 August on the <a href="http://www.johnlewisgiftlist.com">John Lewis website</a>, using list number 559927.</p>

<p>We would also really appreciate contributions for the afternoon tea following the service. If you would like to bring something, please let us know what you intend to bring.</p>
<p><i>A form will be available here closer to the date.</i></p>